%% Scania — Service browse + select (SECM catalog + PIM-SPISA details) per selected vehicle (POC)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Fleet Customer
    participant Yves as Yves (Service UI / PDP)
    participant SecmZed as Zed (ScaniaSecmService)
    participant SecmC as SECM Client
    participant SECM as SECM (Service Catalog)
    participant SpisaZed as Zed (ScaniaSpisaDetail)
    participant SpisaC as PIM-SPISA Client
    participant SPISA as PIM-SPISA (Service Details)

    Note over User,SPISA: Services & prices are NOT in the Spryker catalog — sourced live per vehicle (SD-001)
    User->>Yves: View services for selected vehicle
    Yves->>SecmZed: getCompatibleServices(vehicleRef)
    SecmZed->>SecmC: fetchServices(vehicleRef)
    SecmC->>SECM: GET /services?vehicle=… (REST, sync)
    SECM-->>SecmC: Up to ~100 compatible services + prices
    SecmC-->>SecmZed: ServiceTransfer collection (with price)
    SecmZed-->>Yves: Service list (only compatible shown)
    Yves-->>User: Render service list

    User->>Yves: Open a service (PDP)
    Yves->>SpisaZed: getServiceDetail(serviceRef)
    SpisaZed->>SpisaC: fetchDetail(serviceRef)
    SpisaC->>SPISA: GET /service-details?ref=… (REST, sync)
    SPISA-->>SpisaC: Description, images, (config payload — SD-002)
    SpisaC-->>SpisaZed: DetailTransfer
    SpisaZed-->>Yves: Merge SECM price + SPISA detail
    Yves-->>User: Render service PDP (price locked at add-to-cart)
    Note right of Yves: Future — 1–2 step wizard via Configurable Product (SD-002);<br/>optional SSP service date/time on PDP (Future)
